Package: TMscoreAlign
Type: Package
Title: TMscoreAlign: Protein Structure Alignment using TM-score
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kevin Zhu
Maintainer: Kevin Zhu <kevqyzhu@gmail.com>
Description: 
    The TMscoreAlign package provides tools for performing protein structure 
    alignment using the TM-score metric. It includes functions for optimizing 
    alignments, calculating TM-scores and RMSD, and visualizing aligned 
    structures. The alignment optimization is based on the L-BFGS-B 
    minimization algorithm.
